      • FASTCornerDetector

        public FASTCornerDetector(int threshold,
                  int fastNNumber)
        Creates FAST Corner Detector
        Parameters:
        threshold - Integer for Threshold value.
        fastNNumber - Integer n. Fast algorithm Tests whether there are n contiguous Pixels int the circle which are all darker, or all brighter than Pixel p. This Test does not generalize well for n < 12. There for n can only range from 9 to 12.
